data.description: Are you a veteran who could use an assumable VA loan with a 2.75% interest rate? Are you looking for a large, quiet home in a wonderful neighborhood? Come see us! Sellers have filled this home with love and laughter over the past seven years, and say they have the sweetest neighbors in the world! Sellers are motivated and looking to help the next owners enjoy a wonderful home as well. Requesting a 24-hour notice before showings. We look forward to hearing from you!
